{"tid":2299720,"cid":6,"subCid":0,"title":"男友跟朋友分享與我做愛的心得","createTime":"2020-11-25T03:59:31.000Z","updateTime":"2020-11-25T10:13:10.000Z","uid":136116,"like":2,"dislike":32,"uniUserReply":23,"replies":[{"pid":"f530cba3fa9946933e7ef138c1371a430294dfb6","tid":2299720,"uid":136116,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-25T03:59:31.000Z","msg":"男友中意大奶妹<br />\n偏偏我是骨感bcup女孩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n昨天因為他喝醉點了外賣<br />\n拿他手機看時看到跟朋友的對話<br />\n平常都沒看過也不檢查手機的<br />\n看到朋友問他<br />\n你跟她做愛1到10分給幾分<br />\n他說9.5 剩下0.5是因為奶太小<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n真的很無言<br />\n還沒在一起時<br />\n外觀看就知道我奶的尺寸了吧<br />\n還是我的奶是塞在內褲裡面<br />\n再點開相簿<br />\n裡面也是一堆網美大奶照並且會一起分享<br />\n我知道人也會欣賞美的事物<br />\n但每個都有女友的人還會說哇 好想x我<br />\n這個我可以 看到就感覺快去了 想身寸（？<br />\n重點是 往上滑<br />\n看到還沒在一起前竟然有偷拍我的腿照<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n還傳給群組男生好朋友一起分享<br />\n在一起後 討論說跟我做起來的感覺如何<br />\n好不開心<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"be8d3235917dff97750924f9ff4781a576336ebf","tid":2299720,"uid":1082,"like":15,"dislike":0,"score":15,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-25T04:00:29.000Z","msg":"ptt 都唔放過<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d2ae6cac27fbfdc744622901d30e179e459c3b97","tid":2299720,"uid":128057,"like":9,"dislike":0,"score":9,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2020-11-25T04:01:50.000Z","msg":"我男朋友都嫌我jer細"},{"pid":"073eece307363559fe3f7ef9993fc187b1bdd56d","tid":2299720,"uid":91667,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-25T04:01:58.000Z","msg":"開心share, 好過share 叫雞心得呀"},{"pid":"a7014eedafd035fa7ac16511e4f0094580dd1997","tid":2299720,"uid":234509,"like":0,"dislike":0